title: Corel Paint Shop Pro X Photo retail (Lexar Edition)
description:
I am uploading Corel Paint Shop Pro X full retail. This version is bundled with Lexar flash cards (in my case Lexar Professional 300x UDMA CF 8GB). Some features:

- full English version 10.10 (the newest "original" version is 10.03 - available thru patches). It cannot be installed as an upgrade of the regular version, so please  uninstall theold PSPX.
- full retail version, does not need any serial number, does not call home. etc. but:
- there is an popup window "buy PSP XII") when you close the application. It is not partilarly annoying but I will appreciate if you know the way I can rid of it.  
- in some places of the program written Corel in cooperation with Lexar

Enjoy!

PS In the afternoon I will upload Lexar Image Rescue 3  which was also bundled with the card.
